{"type": "article", "id": 25971, "title": "极简沙发床", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-26T07:35:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 55, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702162631OfucVp4lBRmhUP58.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是 <a href=\"http://konstantin-grcic.com/\">Konstantin Grcic</a> 为 <a href=\"http://www.classicon.com/\">Classicon</a> 所设计的一款沙发床，名叫 Ulisse。它的基座由橡木和胡桃木制成，通过滚轴可以自由调节靠背角度。造型让人想起来自非洲和日本的美学设计，精简的同时强调着做工和材质的选择。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021626286clT8jAo7LuFBizv.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.78117359\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162629v3clbm92J8IeFBHf.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59413203\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162630tco9CWdKZSIjED2T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.78850856\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162630b5hR3LAuB9fHrvcO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62347188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}